headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Declasse Drift Yosemite
content: Unleash your red-necked rage, throw your cans of Pißwasser from the window, give whoever took your space the finger and get gone. Now what? Just sit back, relax and know the Drift Yosemite’s slammed suspension means you’ll have a belly full of roadkill in no time. Sure, it only has room for one passenger upfront, but at least you can take your mom and cousin for a drive.
